Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SUB BY DESTROYKING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在看著我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中 只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡你擁抱我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛！ 原來在家中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一點便可和舞在夢中…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  到底是誰！ 真是吵耳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同級生第一話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夏天的終結時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡現正外出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請於十年後再打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡！？ 是我  一哉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙！ 一哉嗎  蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在暑假的時候這麼早打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件對於我非常重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生大事要跟你談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚麼也不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我現在就要去見阿舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  太冷酷了 吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後還有機會  先跟我見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 白 了  無論如何我要先收線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定了！ 1 1 時在車站前見！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來今天是來美的生 日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪…一哉那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奮鬥！ 奮鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  又是來偷看女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有下賤的人才會做出偷窺這事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 自 己心虛才這樣說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙  你裸體也好  這一身肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也不會來偷看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田徑部的巴比傳出去的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴比說的… 隨你怎樣想也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  寫一封回信好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼信？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美穗啊  她很煩惱呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子那麼純情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這會傷害她的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 白 了  我也是個溫柔的男 人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙那傢伙  一點也沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像個男孩一樣  比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞是個最好的佳麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有女人味  怎樣做也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今個暑假一定要跟她約會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞！ 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就位！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸岡渡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用 色迷迷的眼光看著阿舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是背負 學校名譽的紅牌運動員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知你 自 己是甚麼身份嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山上的鮮花  你採得到手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你慘痛失敗之前放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健兒  你憑甚麼對我這樣說？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對阿舞來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個與別不同的男 人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遲早都會明 白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼話？ 這傢伙到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美穗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…？ 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我做一束 3 千元的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做 1 萬元豪華型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 白 了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是罰你遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知我花了 大半個暑假做兼職嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 了 能跟阿舞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個美妙的暑假回憶這點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真嗎？ 收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞是位真真正正的千金小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你合不來的  你只會流淚收場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 白嗎？ 面對現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來美也沒有向你表示過甚麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  今天是來美的生 日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已決定送甚麼生 日 禮物了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久候了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大贈送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那多謝了  再見  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借你的電單車給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 一哉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信已看過了 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看過了  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呀  真羞人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家害羞的啊  用信回復我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美…美穗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哉！ 這麼遲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…看看這個！ 生 日 快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哉  你真是的… 謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這束花很貴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒有甚麼作回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就… 給我一個吻也吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可擁抱我的話更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要呀  一哉常常跟我說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生甚麼事？ 阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之是一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼炎熱的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給人當作木偶般玩弄…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HeIlo！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  午安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哉他最善用繩索及洋燭的玩法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  不過我也喜歡熄了 燈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點著大量洋燭的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來他們就只差一線還沒超越吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能再思前想後了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要盡快跟阿舞約會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡看這類小說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常到這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是經常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因要應付考試…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我到外面散心好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時也要輕鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這… 我要參加同學會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要學鋼琴和茶道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事情要做…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是甚麼答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累！ 不能集中精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說吧…來美…來美她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一哉只說了 那麼一 句話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道  去到酒店後被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說完便回來了 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奮鬥！ 奮鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都流著青春的熱汗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確如巴比所說的事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加點努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定可在這範圍內 出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  暑假也不睡多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟每日都到學校來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是平時經常偷懶的原因呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對於需要上課的學校很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不用上課的學校我就十分喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿意了 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟用這種借口  有其他目 的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  怎說你也是閒著的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…有件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中同學  請跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  再見！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙要說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 白 了 嗎？ 田中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健兒跟阿舞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞！ 不要在這人面前展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要想辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  跟我來好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸媽要你停止參加田徑運動！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退出體育部  專心讀書準備考試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經高中三年班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸媽所說的也是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你退出 田徑部之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會有點像回一個女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  我是認真跟你相量的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常有女孩在身邊便覺幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎會呢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  退出 田徑部的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以想像到甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由中一開始到現在高校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的比賽開始前為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的比賽  一定要走完它的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成它吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續田徑練習吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要理會雙親說甚麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑美沙一向的 自信去做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是最好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…？ 竟從她的口 中說出謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是生病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那樣叫好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是非常羞人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也要鼓起勇氣說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我美穗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我美穗…想約你去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是看浪漫的愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待你的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲木美穗字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美穗  可以靜點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檢點些！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  你對美穗做過甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有…那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚她打電話來的時候一直在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生甚麼事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是… 那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想哭的人是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這約會竟會如此收場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在想甚麼鬼主意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？ 阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美穗跟你一向交往的女孩是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次你弄哭她  就不會有下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底你喜歡的是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要問吧… 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說清楚呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這… 就是你  美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙你是我最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？ 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BYE BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞  BYE BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BYE BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次推不掉那約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟健兒交往的事是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說這些話  是謊言…那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男 人要有氣力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有氣力的話就最好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家勢及財產只是次要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不施予我  MY SON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡已沒有氣力 了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那火飛射出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那火飛射出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一節是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體出現於少女的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的胸於少女的乳房上搖動…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這彈力 了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從前於我想像過那校服之下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這彈力 了！ 年青人感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如他所說般的場面中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一面憧景著…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去南之島好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矢負町遊樂場那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說剛在南之島開 了 一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WATERPARK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去玩玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今個星期五下午 1 時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遊樂場等你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天安排了 學鋼琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:15:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷一次懶不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期五在遊樂場見！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然又是喜歡死纏爛打型的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事！ 這一點點的傷不算是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做…做甚麼？ 停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧！ 等一會才回來取回單車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼羞人！ 放我下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你放我下來呀！ 很痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢材！ 阿渡放我下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再劇烈擺動  傷口 只會更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變成跛子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽已經接近了 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要小心保護雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的胸部真巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣說也不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的膝蓋骨因練習過度才成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就停止跑步練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不做手術的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再任性了！ 老師這樣擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙你已經盡 了 力  就這樣算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫好雙腳後  再入普通的大學…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠 了！ 你們放心好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我是諸岡渡… 馬戈老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會我的話  晚上會適合些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙？ 是…立即就來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟有此事！ 是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  為何叫我來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中同學有話要跟你一個人說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽她訴說了  可能會有大的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定只有你才能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在教員 室那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在她身邊吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正處於最痛苦的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早操的途中跌倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然會變成這樣  真是難以致信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬戈老師已告訴了 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是個蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為全力 以赴的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而變成再也不能跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…只有阿渡你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾向我說過憑自 己的 自信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子總算可達成爸媽的希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要呀！ 不要說這些話！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都擔心你的健康…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明 白！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我須然不太清楚  若醫好了 的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是可以再繼續跑步嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都這樣說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的最後機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把這痛楚一直忍耐到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有人明 白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  美沙… 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也只不過是因為擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是我  不能跟健康的你吵咀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多 麼的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能再跑步也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是說你 自 己就此完結的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的肌肉 結實嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很柔軟… 太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡… 真羞人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.99,0:23:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.99,0:24:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.91,0:24:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿渡  阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.34,0:25:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 日後
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.71,0:25:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙向田徑部提交了 退出書
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.12,0:25:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入秋之後在街上遇到美沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.29,0:25:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午安  阿渡！ 很久沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我一會好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.37,0:25:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你已經做了 手術
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.74,0:25:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已沒事了  我想很快便可上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.01,0:25:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？ 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.61,0:25:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.65,0:25:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自 己也覺得不可思議的堅持起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.08,0:25:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎會這樣呢？ 阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.59,0:25:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.92,0:25:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.19,0:26:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都以為田徑就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.36,0:26:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我發現了 另一件更激發我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.97,0:26:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.57,0:26:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.97,0:26:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 吧！ 有甚麼事竟然可以激發
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.27,0:26:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像美沙你那樣鬥心強的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.58,0:26:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝你  阿渡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.65,0:26:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.42,0:26:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次… 下一次到你家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.16,0:26:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以跑步呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.36,0:26:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過… 美沙這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.43,0:26:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起話來總算像個女人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.14,0:26:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼會這樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.04,0:28:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回予告
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.64,0:29:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救為愛情而煩惱的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.38,0:29:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.11,0:29:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸岡渡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.85,0:29:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟阿舞約好了的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.72,0:29:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在然在會面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.35,0:29:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣沖沖的向我走過來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.95,0:29:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.79,0:29:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可見到這衝擊性的場面
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.26,0:29:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿舞… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.66,0:29:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿吸引力的同級生 2
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.10,0:29:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要收看呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.30,0:29:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次跟裡美在公園裡…
